title: Should Projects Be Able to Control Their NFT SVGs?
body: Community tokens will have SVG images associated with them. The ERC-721 contracts created by the RadicleRegistry will define a default implementation for how these SVGs are generated, but an open question is whether or not projects should be allowed select/create their own implementation.
author: 0x0630a42785B8A92205A492B3092279529990ED0C
